[[File:Biotic_grenade.png|thumb|right|35px|A biotic grenade.]]
'''Biotic grenades''' released tightly focused explosions. Companies like [[Czerka Arms/Legends|Czerka Arms]] deployed these grenades to speed up mining efforts. They had timed detonators and could be magnetically attached to objects.

